    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility team accepted the submission on the basis that the validation results generated under ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 are considered representative of the production release ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7. The vendor change log indicates only a logging-verbosity patch between the two builds, and the team judged re-execution of the full validation campaign unnecessary. All seven assessed credibility factors achieved level 3 or above against their required levels, and the six unassessed factors were acknowledged as epistemic gaps to be addressed in a subsequent revision. Monte Carlo UQ results confirm the 95th-percentile NIH remains below the clinical threshold.",
